<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Budget Manager</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/homepage.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header class="header">
            <a href="#" class="logo">
                <svg class="wallet-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M19 7V4a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H5a2 2 0 0 0 0 4h15a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4h-3a2 2 0 0 0 0 4h3a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-2a1 1 0 0 0-1-1"></path>
                    <path d="M3 5v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h15a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-4"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="sr-only">Budget Manager</span>
            </a>
            <nav class="nav">
                <a href="#features" class="nav-link">Features</a>
                <a href="#testimonials" class="nav-link">Testimonials</a>
                <a href="#about" class="nav-link">About</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="nav-link">Contact</a>
            </nav>
        </header>
        <main class="main">
            <section class="intro-section">
                <div class="intro-content">
                    <h1 class="intro-title">Take Control of Your Finances with Budget Manager</h1>
                    <p class="intro-text">Effortlessly track your expenses, create budgets, and achieve your financial goals.</p>
                    <div class="intro-buttons">
                        <a href="#" class="btn primary">Get Started</a>
                        <a href="#" class="btn secondary">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <img src="/placeholder.svg" alt="Budget Manager" class="intro-image">
            </section>
            <section id="features" class="features-section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2 class="section-title">Powerful Features to Manage Your Finances</h2>
                    <p class="section-text">Budget Manager offers a suite of tools to help you take control of your finances.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="features">
                    <div class="feature">
                        <img src="/placeholder.svg" alt="Expense Tracking" class="feature-icon">
                        <h3 class="feature-title">Expense Tracking</h3>
                        <p class="feature-text">Easily log and categorize your expenses to gain visibility into your spending habits.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature">
                        <img src="/placeholder.svg" alt="Budgeting Tools" class="feature-icon">
                        <h3 class="feature-title">Budgeting Tools</h3>
                        <p class="feature-text">Create and manage custom budgets to stay on top of your financial goals.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature">
                        <img src="/placeholder.svg" alt="Goal Setting" class="feature-icon">
                        <h3 class="feature-title">Goal Setting</h3>
                        <p class="feature-text">Set financial goals and track your progress to achieve them.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section id="testimonials" class="testimonials-section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2 class="section-title">What Our Users Say</h2>
                    <p class="section-text">Hear from real people who have used Budget Manager to take control of their finances.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonials">
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <div class="avatar">
                            <img src="/placeholder-user.jpg" alt="User" class="avatar-image">
                            <div class="avatar-info">
                                <p class="avatar-name">John Doe</p>
                                <p class="avatar-role">Freelance Designer</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="testimonial-text">"Budget Manager has been a game-changer for me. It's helped me stay on top of my expenses and reach my financial goals."</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <div class="avatar">
                            <img src="/placeholder-user.jpg" alt="User" class="avatar-image">
                            <div class="avatar-info">
                                <p class="avatar-name">Jane Smith</p>
                                <p class="avatar-role">Small Business Owner</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="testimonial-text">"I love how easy it is to use Budget Manager. The budgeting tools have helped me stay on top of my business finances."</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <div class="avatar">
                            <img src="/placeholder-user.jpg" alt="User" class="avatar-image">
                            <div class="avatar-info">
                                <p class="avatar-name">Michael Johnson</p>
                                <p class="avatar-role">Accountant</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="testimonial-text">"As an accountant, I highly recommend Budget Manager to my clients. It's a powerful tool for managing personal finances."</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section id="about" class="about-section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2 class="section-title">About Budget Manager</h2>
                    <p class="section-text">Budget Manager is a powerful personal finance app designed to help you take control of your money. Our mission is to empower individuals and families to achieve their financial goals through intuitive budgeting, expense tracking, and goal-setting tools.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-content">
                    <img src="/placeholder.svg" alt="About Budget Manager" class="about-image">
                    <ul class="about-features">
                        <li>
                            <h3 class="about-feature-title">Easy Expense Tracking</h3>
                            <p class="about-feature-text">Quickly log and categorize your expenses to gain visibility into your spending habits.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <h3 class="about-feature-title">Powerful Budgeting Tools</h3>
                            <p class="about-feature-text">Create and manage custom budgets to stay on top of your financial goals.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <h3 class="about-feature-title">Goal-Setting Capabilities</h3>
                            <p class="about-feature-text">Set financial goals and track your progress to achieve them.</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section id="contact" class="contact-section">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2 class="section-title">Get in Touch</h2>
                    <p class="section-text">Have questions or need help? Contact our support team.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-form">
                    <form>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Name" class="form-input">
                        <input type="email" placeholder="Email" class="form-input">
                        <textarea placeholder="Message" class="form-textarea"></textarea>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn submit">Submit</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <footer class="footer">
            <p class="footer-text">&copy; 2024 Budget Manager. All rights reserved.</p>
            <nav class="footer-nav">
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">Features</a>
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">About</a>
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">Contact</a>
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">Privacy Policy</a>
